From: stigmergy-mcp-benchmark fix
Subject: [PATCH] fix: detect Content Transfer in Run B handoff messages

The Run B (message-passing) handoff string failed to match any
CONTENT_TRANSFER_PATTERNS regex, causing the entire handoff payload
to fall through to COORDINATION_PATTERNS where it matched
"previous agent produced" and was misclassified as Coordination
Instructions.

This patch:
1. Adds an explicit [content-transfer] marker to the handoff template,
   mirroring the existing TOOL_DEFINITION_MARKER pattern.
2. Adds two regex patterns to CONTENT_TRANSFER_PATTERNS: one for the
   new marker, one for the existing "--- Agent N (role) output ---"
   block separator already emitted by messagePassingHandoff.

After this patch, Run B Content Transfer is measured correctly and
inter-agent savings calculations reflect the actual O(N^2) growth
in message-passing versus O(N) growth in stigmergy.

---
 packages/classifier/src/categories.ts    | 4 +++-
 packages/executors/src/agent-prompt.ts   | 2 +-
 2 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/packages/classifier/src/categories.ts b/packages/classifier/src/categories.ts
--- a/packages/classifier/src/categories.ts
+++ b/packages/classifier/src/categories.ts
@@ -29,11 +29,13 @@ export const COORDINATION_PATTERNS: RegExp[] = [
 /**
  * Content transfer patterns — indicate work product being passed between agents.
  */
 export const CONTENT_TRANSFER_PATTERNS: RegExp[] = [
+  /\[content-transfer\]/i,
+  /---\s*Agent\s+\d+\s+\(.+?\)\s+output\s*---/i,
   /\bhere\s+is\s+(the|my)\s+(output|result|analysis|findings|code|review)\b/i,
   /\bthe\s+following\s+(was|is)\s+(produced|generated|found)\s+by\b/i,
   /\bagent\s+\w+('s)?\s+(output|result|analysis|response)\s*:/i,
   /\b(previous|prior)\s+agent('s)?\s+(output|work|response)\b/i,
-  /^```[\s\S]{200,}/m, // Large code blocks (>= 200 chars, likely work product)
+  /^```[\s\S]{200,}/m,
 ];
 
 /**
diff --git a/packages/executors/src/agent-prompt.ts b/packages/executors/src/agent-prompt.ts
--- a/packages/executors/src/agent-prompt.ts
+++ b/packages/executors/src/agent-prompt.ts
@@ -53,11 +53,11 @@ export function messagePassingHandoff(
   if (previousOutputs.length === 0) return '';
 
   const parts = previousOutputs.map(
     (p, i) => `--- Agent ${i + 1} (${p.agentRole}) output ---\n${p.output}`,
   );
 
   return [
-    `The previous agent produced the following. Please review and continue:`,
+    `[content-transfer] Prior agent outputs follow. Continue from where they left off.`,
     ``,
     ...parts,
   ].join('\n');
 }
